OL,3,CBritish couple in seventies arrested
OL,4,Cby the Taliban in Afghanistan
OL,6,FA British couple in their seventies
OL,7,Fhave been arrested by the Taliban in
OL,8,FAfghanistan, their children say.
OL,10,FPeter Reynolds, 79 and his wife
OL,11,FBarbie, 75, ran educational training
OL,12,Fprojects in the country.
OL,14,FThey were returning home when they
OL,15,Fwere detained earlier this month. It
OL,16,Fis not clear why they have been
OL,17,Farrested.
OL,19,FThe couples' four children wrote a
OL,20,Fletter to the Taliban urging for their
OL,21,Fparents' release.
