OL,6,FThey wrote: "We do not understand the
OL,7,Freasons behind their arrest.
OL,9,F"They have communicated their trust in
OL,10,Fyou, and that as Afghan citizens they
OL,11,Fwill be treated well."
OL,13,FThe couple were married in Kabul in
OL,14,F1970 and have been living and working
OL,15,Fin Afghanistan for almost two decades,
OL,16,Fstaying after the Taliban took over in
OL,17,F2021.
OL,19,F"They became official Afghan citizens
OL,20,Fand have been living there for the
OL,21,Fpast 18 years.
