OL,7,Fhad been teaching young mothers and
OL,8,Fchildren as part of their training
OL,9,Fprojects but women have now been
OL,10,Fbanned from education after the age of
OL,11,F12.
OL,13,FThere are also concerns for Mr
OL,14,FReynold's health and access to his
OL,15,Fheart medication after he had a mini
OL,16,Fstroke.
